                         U.S. Department of Energy
           Office of Congressional and Intergovernmental Affairs
                        1000 Independence Avenue SW
                           Washington, DC 20585

    The mission of the Office of Congressional and Intergovernmental
    Affairs (CI) is to promote Department of Energy (DOE) policies,
    programs and initiatives through liaison, communications,
    coordination and interaction with Congress, State, Tribal, City, and
    County Governments, other Federal agencies, stakeholders, and the
    general public.

